OL,3,CMan fined after rubbish he paid people
OL,4,Cto recycle is fly-tipped
OL,6,FA man who paid three strangers to
OL,7,Frecycle his rubbish has been fined
OL,8,Fnearly #1,400 after it was fly-tipped.
OL,10,FGhazanfar Hussain, 39, of Roseberry
OL,11,FStreet, Rotherham, paid three
OL,12,Fstrangers #350 for a lorry load of
OL,13,Fwaste to be removed, after they were
OL,14,Frecommended by a friend.
OL,16,FThe three men took a second load of
OL,17,Frubbish - agreeing that they would be
OL,18,Fpaid when they returned with a
OL,19,Freceipt, but they never returned.
OL,20,FHussain said he'd not seen them since.
