OL,3,CMan fined after rubbish he paid people
OL,4,Cto recycle is fly-tipped
OL,6,F"Remember, your waste is still your
OL,7,Fresponsibility, even when you've given
OL,8,Fit to someone else."
OL,10,FHussain pleaded guilty to not
OL,11,Fperforming his duty of care and
OL,12,Fmagistrates fined him #550, ordered
OL,13,Fhim to pay #606 costs and a victim
OL,14,Fsurcharge of #220.
